It is the 1172nd year since the ancestreal war

You are a human, 21 years of age, the youngest child of a family said to trace back to a hero of the ancestreal war. You have trained since you were a young child and now, having come of age, set off in search of fame and fortune as a knight errant in the rich and fertile lands of your kin.

Your starting alignment is Lawful.
You are at full health
You have 255 gold
You have a bow and 20 steel arrows
You wield a Broadsword and a Heater shield
You are magic impaired
